data.description: Welcome to 4 Burning Ember Ln, a prime opportunity to own a spacious pool home in Indian Trails. With easy walking access to top schools & the Indian Trails Sports Complex, this residence sits on an oversized, well-manicured 17,000 sqft lot, perfect for family activities. The charming front porch leads to an interior with soaring ceilings, wood-burning fireplace, custom wood trim & artistic touches. The recently renovated kitchen showcases new cabinetry, light fixtures, countertops, sink & faucets. The dining& family rooms provide ample space. The screened-in pool area with bar top seating offers views of the large fenced backyard. New roof (8/2021) & upgraded AC units, this home is move-in ready. Conveniently located near A-rated schools, 15 mins from the beach, world-class golf & I-95.
